      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "そのつもりだったんですけど……",
      "startTime": 204.2445990801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "予定が変わっちゃって\n私だけライブの後はみんなと別行動なんです",
      "startTime": 209.6779324134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "星見まつりをあんなに楽しみにしていたのに\n千紗は見て行かないのか？",
      "startTime": 217.3333426793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、お祭りは見て回ります\nただ、一緒に行く相手はみんなじゃなくて……",
      "startTime": 222.5733065407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、沙季と一緒に行くんだな！\n相変わらず二人は仲がいいな",
      "startTime": 229.9666760127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、相手はお姉ちゃんじゃないです",
      "startTime": 232.9447126389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "なら……地元の友達か？\n東京にいたらなかなか会えないからな",
      "startTime": 239.3666760127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
